gcloud pubsub topics publish news-updated --project liu-search-api-dev --message "{\"app\":\"OneCampus\",\"app_base_url\":\"https:\/\/onecampus.laureate.net\",\"info\":{\"id\":1991,\"first_published_at\":\"2019-06-13T15:13:44.876000+00:00\",\"last_published_at\":\"2020-05-20T05:38:25.768977+00:00\",\"image_url\":\"https:\/\/liu-wagtail-dev.azurewebsites.net\/images\/la9DOC2iq5CwA3erNgCiKNb3sec%3D\/1319\/original\/WOBI_London.png\",\"en\":{\"title\":\"Save the Date: World Business Forum London 2019\",\"description\":\"<p>The World Business Forum brings together top leaders, entrepreneurs, and thought leaders from around the world. Through OneCampus, you have a front row seat at this global event. <b>The London 2019 event will be streamed on OneCampus for 10 days only, September 23 to October 2.<\/b> See presentations by experts such as Michael Porter, Susan David, Simon Sinek, Marcus Buckingham, and Steven Covey on topics including competitive strategy, consumer psychology, personal performance, and the future of work. Join in a discussion with your colleagues on OneCampus and see how you can use these ideas to further your own career.<\/p><p>Visit OneCampus today to subscribe to the World Business Forum London email list and <a href='https:\/\/onecampus.laureate.net\/wobi\/home\/#\/v2\/events\/wobi\/1981'>see more information<\/a> about this exclusive event.<\/p>\",\"short_description\":\"<p>Coming in September, exclusively on OneCampus \u2013 World Business Forum London<\/p>\"},\"es\":{\"title\":\"Reserva la Fecha: World Business Forum Londres 2019\",\"description\":\"<p>El World Business Forum re\u00fane a los principales l\u00edderes, empresarios y l\u00edderes de pensamiento de todo el mundo. A trav\u00e9s de OneCampus, tendr\u00e1s un asiento de primera fila en este exclusivo evento global. <b>El evento de Londres 2019 se transmitir\u00e1 en OneCampus por solamente 10 d\u00edas, del 23 de septiembre al 2 de octubre.<\/b> Podr\u00e1s ver presentaciones de expertos como Michael Porter, Susan David, Simon Sinek, Marcus Buckingham y Steven Covey discutiendo temas como estrategia competitiva, psicolog\u00eda del consumidor, desempe\u00f1o personal y el futuro del trabajo. \u00danete a la discusi\u00f3n con tus compa\u00f1eros en OneCampus y descubre c\u00f3mo puedes usar estas ideas para impulsar tu propia carrera.<\/p><p>Visita OneCampus hoy para suscribirte a la lista de correo electr\u00f3nico del World Business Forum Londres y <a href='https:\/\/onecampus.laureate.net\/wobi\/home\/#\/v2\/events\/wobi\/1981'>obtener m\u00e1s informaci\u00f3n<\/a> sobre este exclusivo evento.<\/p>\",\"short_description\":\"<p>Disponible en septiembre, exclusivamente en OneCampus - World Business Forum Londres<\/p>\"},\"pt\":{\"title\":\"Guarde a data: World Business Forum, Londres, 2019\",\"description\":\"<p>O World Business Forum apresenta, em um s\u00f3 evento, grandes l\u00edderes, empreendedores e l\u00edderes de opini\u00e3o de todo o mundo. Atrav\u00e9s do OneCampus, voc\u00ea tem privil\u00e9gio nesse evento global. <b>A edi\u00e7\u00e3o em Londres em 2019 ser\u00e1 exibida por<\/b> <b><i>streaming<\/i><\/b><b> no OneCampus por somente 10 dias, de 23 de setembro a 2 de outubro.<\/b> Assista \u00e0s apresenta\u00e7\u00f5es de especialistas tais como Michael Porter, Susan David, Simon Sinek, Marcus Buckingham e Steven Covey sobre t\u00f3picos que incluem estrat\u00e9gia competitiva, psicologia do consumo, desempenho pessoal e o futuro do trabalho. Participe de uma discuss\u00e3o com seus colegas no OneCampus e veja como voc\u00ea pode empregar essas ideias na sua pr\u00f3pria carreira no futuro.<\/p><p>Visite o OneCampus hoje, inscreva-se na lista de e-mails do World Business Forum Londres e <a href='https:\/\/onecampus.laureate.net\/wobi\/home\/#\/v2\/events\/wobi\/1981'>veja mais informa\u00e7\u00f5es<\/a> sobre este evento exclusivo.<\/p>\",\"short_description\":\"<p>Em setembro, exclusivamente no OneCampus \u2013 World Business Forum, Londres<\/p>\"},\"related_images\":[]},\"site_url\":\"https:\/\/liu-wagtail-dev.azurewebsites.net\",\"url_path\":\"\/home\/onecampus-portal\/news\/news-folder-oc\/save-the-date-world-business-forum-london-2019\/\",\"type\":\"news\",\"tags\":[],\"slug\":\"save-the-date-world-business-forum-london-2019\",\"parent_slug\":\"news-folder-oc\"}"